{
  "texts": [
    "The zero-shot experiment files are in cloud_scripts/gcp/experiments/zero_shot/ and cloud_scripts/gcp/experiments/ zero_shot_packing/.",
    "Batch sizes are set to run on a GPU with at least 20 GB RAM.",
    "The GPU must support the data types needed for QLoRA, e.g., an L4 GPU.",
    "Figure 6 can be reproduced by running the notebooks in analysis/fit_posteriors/zero_shot and analysis/fit_posteriors/zero_shot_packing and then the notebook, analysis/results/posterior_pred.ipynb.",
    "The Mistral 7B model is Mistral-7B-v0.3, the non-instruction-trained model."
  ]
}